/**
 * Utilit function to generate day wise series
 * @param {*} baseval
 * @param {*} count
 * @param {*} yrange
 */function generateDayWiseTimeSeries(baseval,count,yrange){var i=0;var series=[];while(i<count){var x=baseval;var y=Math.floor(Math.random()*(yrange.max-yrange.min+1))+yrange.min;series.push({x:x,y:y});baseval+=86400000;i++;}return series;}/**
